Detailed Description

Implementation of the Bump function. f(x) = frac{abs(sum(cos(x_i)^4) - 2prod(cos(x_i)^2))}{sqrt(sum{i=1}^n i*(x_i)^2)}; prod x_i > 0.75; sum x_i < 15*n/2.
